<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="やさしい買い物 — 高齢者と視覚障害者のためのネットスーパー。大きな文字、音声操作、シンプルな操作で安心してお買い物できます。" />
  <title>やさしい買い物 | 高齢者・視覚障害者向けネットスーパー</title>

  <!-- Google Fonts: Noto Serif JP + Noto Sans JP -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;700;900&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    /* ===================================================
       CSS VARIABLES & RESET
    =================================================== */
    :root {
      --bg:           #faf8f4;
      --bg-card:      #ffffff;
      --bg-header:    #ffffff;
      --bg-hero:      #f0ede6;
      --text-primary: #1a1a1a;
      --text-secondary:#4a4a4a;
      --text-muted:   #767676;
      --accent:       #c0392b;
      --accent-hover: #922b21;
      --accent-light: #fadbd8;
      --green:        #27ae60;
      --green-hover:  #1e8449;
      --border:       #d5cfc7;
      --shadow:       0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      --shadow-lg:    0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      --radius:       12px;
      --radius-lg:    20px;
      --font-base:    18px;
      --transition:   0.2s ease;
      --sidebar-w:    360px;
    }

    /* HIGH CONTRAST MODE */
    body.high-contrast {
      --bg:           #000000;
      --bg-card:      #111111;
      --bg-header:    #000000;
      --bg-hero:      #0a0a0a;
      --text-primary: #ffffff;
      --text-secondary:#eeeeee;
      --text-muted:   #cccccc;
      --accent:       #ffdd57;
      --accent-hover: #ffc400;
      --accent-light: #332e00;
      --green:        #00ff88;
      --green-hover:  #00cc6a;
      --border:       #555555;
      --shadow:       0 2px 16px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      --shadow-lg:    0 8px 32px rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    }

    /* DARK MODE */
    body.dark-mode {
      --bg:           #1a1a1f;
      --bg-card:      #25252d;
      --bg-header:    #15151a;
      --bg-hero:      #1f1f28;
      --text-primary: #f0eee8;
      --text-secondary:#c8c4bc;
      --text-muted:   #918d85;
      --accent:       #e74c3c;
      --accent-hover: #c0392b;
      --accent-light: #3d1a18;
      --green:        #2ecc71;
      --green-hover:  #27ae60;
      --border:       #3a3a44;
      --shadow:       0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
      --shadow-lg:    0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
      font-size: var(--font-base);
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      line-height: 1.7;
      transition: background var(--transition), color var(--transition);
    }

    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    button { cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; }
    ul { list-style: none; }

    /* Skip link for screen readers */
    .skip-link {
      position: absolute;
      top: -100px;
      left: 0;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      border-radius: 0 0 var(--radius) 0;
      z-index: 9999;
      transition: top 0.2s;
    }
    .skip-link:focus { top: 0; }

    /* ===================================================
       LAYOUT HELPERS
    =================================================== */
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }
    .section { padding: 64px 0; }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .section-subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    /* ===================================================
       HEADER
    =================================================== */
    #main-header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 500;
      background: var(--bg-header);
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      transition: background var(--transition);
    }

    .header-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .logo-icon {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      background: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .logo-text {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .logo-sub {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      display: block;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    /* Desktop nav */
    .main-nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }
    .main-nav a {
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      transition: background var(--transition), color var(--transition);
    }
    .main-nav a:hover,
    .main-nav a:focus {
      background: var(--accent-light);
      color: var(--accent);
      outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    .header-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .cart-btn {
      position: relative;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      transition: background var(--transition), transform var(--transition);
    }
    .cart-btn:hover, .cart-btn:focus {
      background: var(--accent-hover);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      outline: 3px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }
    .cart-count {
      position: absolute;
      top: -6px;
      right: -6px;
      background: var(--green);
      color: #fff;
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* Hamburger */
    .hamburger {
      display: none;
      background: none;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 5px;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
    }
    .hamburger span {
      display: block;
      width: 22px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--text-primary);
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: var(--transition);
    }

    /* Mobile nav overlay */
    .mobile-nav {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 800;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    .mobile-nav.open { display: block; }
    .mobile-nav-panel {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 80%;
      max-width: 320px;
      height: 100%;
      background: var(--bg-card);
      padding: 32px 24px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }
    .mobile-nav-close {
      align-self: flex-end;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .mobile-nav-panel a {
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: background var(--transition);
    }
    .mobile-nav-panel a:hover,
    .mobile-nav-panel a:focus {
      background: var(--accent-light);
      color: var(--accent);
      outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
    }

    /* ===================================================
       ACCESSIBILITY TOOLBAR (floating)
    =================================================== */
    #a11y-toolbar {
      position: fixed;
      right: 20px;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      z-index: 450;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 12px 8px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }

    .a11y-btn {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
      transition: background var(--transition), color var(--transition), border-color var(--transition);
      line-height: 1.1;
    }
    .a11y-btn .a11y-icon { font-size: 1.3rem; }
    .a11y-btn .a11y-label { font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
    .a11y-btn:hover,
    .a11y-btn:focus {
      background: var(--accent-light);
      color: var(--accent);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }
    .a11y-btn.active {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      border-color: var(--accent);
    }

    /* ===================================================
       HERO
    =================================================== */
    #hero {
      background: var(--bg-hero);
      padding: 72px 0 64px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    #hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -60px;
      right: -60px;
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-light) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 48px;
    }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: var(--accent-light);
      color: var(--accent);
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero-desc {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .hero-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 18px 32px;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      transition: background var(--transition), transform var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(192,57,43,0.3);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover, .btn-primary:focus {
      background: var(--accent-hover);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(192,57,43,0.4);
      outline: 3px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 3px;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      padding: 16px 28px;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      transition: background var(--transition), border-color var(--transition), transform var(--transition);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover, .btn-secondary:focus {
      background: var(--accent-light);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: var(--accent);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      outline: 3px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 3px;
    }

    /* Hero illustration placeholder */
    .hero-visual {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      height: 320px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 16px;
      font-size: 5rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .hero-visual p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* Stat cards */
    .hero-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    .stat-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 20px 16px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .stat-number {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--accent);
    }
    .stat-label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 4px; }

    /* ===================================================
       VOICE SEARCH
    =================================================== */
    #voice-search {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-top: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
      padding: 40px 0;
    }

    .voice-search-box {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .voice-search-box h2 {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .voice-search-box p {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .search-input-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
      background: var(--bg);
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 8px 8px 8px 20px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    #search-input {
      flex: 1;
      border: none;
      background: transparent;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-family: inherit;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      outline: none;
      padding: 8px 0;
    }
    #search-input::placeholder { color: var(--text-muted); }

    .mic-btn {
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: none;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      transition: background var(--transition), transform var(--transition);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(192,57,43,0.3);
    }
    .mic-btn:hover, .mic-btn:focus {
      background: var(--accent-hover);
      transform: scale(1.05);
      outline: 3px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }
    .mic-btn.listening {
      background: var(--green);
      animation: pulse-mic 1s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse-mic {
      0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(39,174,96,0.4); }
      50%       { box-shadow: 0 0 0 12px rgba(39,174,96,0); }
    }

    .voice-status {
      margin-top: 12px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      min-height: 1.5em;
    }
    .voice-status.active { color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; }

    /* ===================================================
       CATEGORY TABS
    =================================================== */
    .category-tabs {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }
    .cat-tab {
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--bg-card);
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all var(--transition);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .cat-tab:hover, .cat-tab:focus {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: var(--accent);
      outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }
    .cat-tab.active {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      border-color: var(--accent);
    }

    /* ===================================================
       PRODUCT GRID
    =================================================== */
    .product-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .product-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      transition: transform var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition), border-color var(--transition);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .product-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      border-color: var(--accent);
    }
    .product-card:focus-within {
      outline: 3px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    .product-img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 200px;
      object-fit: cover;
      background: var(--bg-hero);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 4rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .product-body {
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .product-category {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .product-name {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .product-desc {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .product-price {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .product-price span {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    }

    .add-to-cart-btn {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      background: var(--green);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      transition: background var(--transition), transform var(--transition);
      font-family: inherit;
    }
    .add-to-cart-btn:hover, .add-to-cart-btn:focus {
      background: var(--green-hover);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      outline: 3px solid var(--green);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }
    .add-to-cart-btn:active {
      transform: scale(0.98);
    }

    /* Product card hidden for filter */
    .product-card[data-hidden="true"] {
      display: none;
    }

    /* ===================================================
       いつもの注文 SECTION
    =================================================== */
    #quick-order {
      background: var(--bg-hero);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 40px;
      margin: 0 24px;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      #quick-order { margin: 0 12px; padding: 28px 20px; }
    }

    .quick-order-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .quick-order-icon {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      background: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .quick-order-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .quick-item {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 16px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      transition: border-color var(--transition), transform var(--transition);
    }
    .quick-item:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .quick-item-emoji { font-size: 2.4rem; }
    .quick-item-name  { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); }
    .quick-item-info  { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); }

    .reorder-btn {
      padding: 10px 16px;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      font-family: inherit;
      transition: background var(--transition);
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .reorder-btn:hover, .reorder-btn:focus {
      background: var(--accent-hover);
      outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    /* ===================================================
       AI ASSISTANT CHAT
    =================================================== */
    #ai-assistant {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-top: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
    }

    .chat-container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: var(--bg);
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }

    .chat-header {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .chat-header-icon {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .chat-header-info h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .chat-header-info p  { font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.85; }

    .chat-messages {
      height: 320px;
      overflow-y: auto;
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    .msg {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      max-width: 85%;
    }
    .msg.bot { align-self: flex-start; }
    .msg.user { align-self: flex-end; flex-direction: row-reverse; }

    .msg-avatar {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      align-self: flex-end;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .msg.user .msg-avatar { background: var(--green); }

    .msg-bubble {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px 16px 16px 4px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .msg.user .msg-bubble {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      border-color: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 16px 16px 4px 16px;
    }

    .chat-suggestions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--bg-hero);
    }
    .suggestion-chip {
      padding: 8px 14px;
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      transition: all var(--transition);
      font-family: inherit;
    }
    .suggestion-chip:hover, .suggestion-chip:focus {
      background: var(--accent-light);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: var(--accent);
      outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    .chat-input-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    #chat-input {
      flex: 1;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-family: inherit;
      background: var(--bg-card);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color var(--transition);
    }
    #chat-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
    #chat-input::placeholder { color: var(--text-muted); }

    .chat-send-btn {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: background var(--transition);
      font-family: inherit;
    }
    .chat-send-btn:hover, .chat-send-btn:focus {
      background: var(--accent-hover);
      outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    .typing-indicator {
      display: flex;
      gap: 4px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8px 4px;
    }
    .typing-indicator span {
      width: 8px; height: 8px;
      background: var(--text-muted);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: blink 1.2s infinite;
    }
    .typing-indicator span:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .typing-indicator span:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 80%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scale(1); }
      40%           { opacity: 1;   transform: scale(1.2); }
    }

    /* ===================================================
       FAMILY SUPPORT SECTION
    =================================================== */
    #family-support {
      background: var(--bg-hero);
      border-top: 2px solid var(--border);
    }

    .family-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .family-features {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .family-feature {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .family-feature-icon {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      background: var(--accent-light);
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .family-feature h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .family-feature p  { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }

    .family-visual {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }
    .family-visual-emoji { font-size: 5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .family-visual h3 {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .family-visual p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 24px; }

    /* ===================================================
       CART SIDEBAR
    =================================================== */
    .cart-overlay {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
      z-index: 700;
    }
    .cart-overlay.open { display: block; }

    #cart-sidebar {
      position: fixed;
      right: -420px;
      top: 0;
      width: var(--sidebar-w);
      max-width: 95vw;
      height: 100%;
      background: var(--bg-card);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      z-index: 750;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      transition: right 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);
    }
    #cart-sidebar.open { right: 0; }

    .cart-header {
      padding: 20px 24px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .cart-header h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .cart-close {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background: var(--bg);
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .cart-close:hover, .cart-close:focus {
      background: var(--accent-light);
      color: var(--accent);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    .cart-items {
      flex: 1;
      overflow-y: auto;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .cart-empty {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }
    .cart-empty-icon { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .cart-empty p { font-size: 1rem; }

    .cart-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      background: var(--bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 12px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .cart-item-emoji { font-size: 2rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .cart-item-info { flex: 1; }
    .cart-item-name { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .cart-item-price { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }
    .cart-item-qty {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }
    .qty-btn {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--bg-card);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: all var(--transition);
    }
    .qty-btn:hover, .qty-btn:focus {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      border-color: var(--accent);
      outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 1px;
    }
    .qty-num { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; min-width: 24px; text-align: center; }
    .cart-item-del {
      background: none;
      border: none;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      padding: 4px;
      transition: color var(--transition);
    }
    .cart-item-del:hover, .cart-item-del:focus {
      color: var(--accent);
      outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    .cart-footer {
      border-top: 2px solid var(--border);
      padding: 20px 24px;
    }
    .cart-total {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .cart-total-label { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .cart-total-amount {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--accent);
    }
    .checkout-btn {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 18px;
      background: var(--green);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      transition: background var(--transition);
      font-family: inherit;
    }
    .checkout-btn:hover, .checkout-btn:focus {
      background: var(--green-hover);
      outline: 3px solid var(--green);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    /* ===================================================
       EMERGENCY BUTTON
    =================================================== */
    #emergency-btn {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 30px;
      left: 24px;
      z-index: 450;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(192,57,43,0.4);
      animation: emergency-pulse 3s infinite;
      transition: transform var(--transition);
    }
    #emergency-btn:hover, #emergency-btn:focus {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      outline: 3px solid #fff;
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }
    @keyframes emergency-pulse {
      0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(192,57,43,0.4); }
      50%       { box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(192,57,43,0.7); }
    }

    /* ===================================================
       TOAST NOTIFICATION
    =================================================== */
    #toast {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 100px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(20px);
      background: var(--green);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 9998;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    #toast.show {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
    }

    /* ===================================================
       FOOTER
    =================================================== */
    #main-footer {
      background: var(--bg-header);
      border-top: 2px solid var(--border);
      padding: 48px 0 28px;
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .footer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .footer-brand .logo-text { font-size: 1.3rem; }
    .footer-brand p {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-top: 12px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .footer-col h4 {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .footer-col ul { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    .footer-col a {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      transition: color var(--transition);
    }
    .footer-col a:hover, .footer-col a:focus {
      color: var(--accent);
      outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-top: 24px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .footer-bottom p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-muted); }

    .footer-a11y-badges {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .a11y-badge {
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    /* ===================================================
       RESPONSIVE
    =================================================== */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-visual { height: 200px; }
      .hero-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .family-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      :root { --font-base: 16px; }
      .main-nav { display: none; }
      .hamburger { display: flex; }
      .hero-title { font-size: 1.6rem; }
      .hero-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 10px; }
      .product-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr)); }
      #a11y-toolbar { right: 8px; }
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      #emergency-btn span:last-child { display: none; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .header-inner { padding: 12px 16px; }
      .hero-title { font-size: 1.4rem; }
      .hero-buttons { flex-direction: column; }
      .btn-primary, .btn-secondary { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
      .container { padding: 0 16px; }
    }

    /* Focus visible styles for all interactive elements */
    :focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid var(--accent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    /* Smooth reading mode (large fonts) class */
    body.large-font {
      --font-base: 22px;
    }
    body.xlarge-font {
      --font-base: 26px;
    }

    /* ===================================================
       READ ALOUD HIGHLIGHT
    =================================================== */
    .tts-active { outline: 3px dashed var(--green) !important; }

  </style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- ===== SKIP LINK ===== -->
<a class="skip-link" href="#main-content">メインコンテンツへスキップ</a>

<!-- ===== MOBILE NAV OVERLAY ===== -->
<div class="mobile-nav" id="mobile-nav" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="モバイルメニュー">
  <nav class="mobile-nav-panel">
    <button class="mobile-nav-close" id="mobile-nav-close" aria-label="メニューを閉じる">✕</button>
    <a href="#home" onclick="closeMobileNav()">🏠 ホーム</a>
    <a href="#products" onclick="closeMobileNav()">🛒 商品</a>
    <a href="#quick-order-section" onclick="closeMobileNav()">⭐ いつもの注文</a>
    <a href="#family-support" onclick="closeMobileNav()">👨‍👩‍👧 サポート</a>
    <a href="#contact-section" onclick="closeMobileNav()">📞 お問い合わせ</a>
  </nav>
</div>

<!-- ===== HEADER ===== -->
<header id="main-header" role="banner">
  <div class="header-inner">

    <a href="#" class="logo" aria-label="やさしい買い物 ホームへ">
      <div class="logo-icon" aria-hidden="true">🛍️</div>
      <div class="logo-text">
        やさしい買い物
        <span class="logo-sub">Senior Friendly Shopping</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <nav class="main-nav" aria-label="メインナビゲーション">
      <a href="#home">ホーム</a>
      <a href="#products">商品</a>
      <a href="#quick-order-section">いつもの注文</a>
      <a href="#family-support">サポート</a>
      <a href="#contact-section">お問い合わせ</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="header-actions">
      <button class="cart-btn" id="cart-open-btn" aria-label="カートを開く（0点）" aria-expanded="false">
        🛒 カート
        <span class="cart-count" id="cart-count" aria-live="polite">0</span>
      </button>
      <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger-btn" aria-label="メニューを開く" aria-expanded="false">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </button>
    </div>

  </div>
</header>

<!-- ===== ACCESSIBILITY TOOLBAR ===== -->
<aside id="a11y-toolbar" aria-label="アクセシビリティツール">
  <button class="a11y-btn" id="font-increase-btn" onclick="changeFontSize(1)" aria-label="文字を大きくする">
    <span class="a11y-icon">A+</span>
    <span class="a11y-label">大きく</span>
  </button>
  <button class="a11y-btn" id="font-decrease-btn" onclick="changeFontSize(-1)" aria-label="文字を小さくする">
    <span class="a11y-icon">A-</span>
    <span class="a11y-label">小さく</span>
  </button>
  <button class="a11y-btn" id="dark-mode-btn" onclick="toggleDarkMode()" aria-label="ダークモード切替" aria-pressed="false">
    <span class="a11y-icon">🌙</span>
    <span class="a11y-label">暗め</span>
  </button>
  <button class="a11y-btn" id="contrast-btn" onclick="toggleContrast()" aria-label="ハイコントラスト切替" aria-pressed="false">
    <span class="a11y-icon">◑</span>
    <span class="a11y-label">強調</span>
  </button>
  <button class="a11y-btn" id="tts-btn" onclick="toggleReadAloud()" aria-label="読み上げ機能">
    <span class="a11y-icon">🔊</span>
    <span class="a11y-label">読む</span>
  </button>
</aside>

<!-- ===== MAIN CONTENT ===== -->
<main id="main-content">

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <section id="home" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
    <div id="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-inner">
          <!-- Left side -->
          <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="hero-badge" aria-label="バリアフリー対応">
              ♿ バリアフリー対応ショップ
            </div>
            <h1 class="hero-title" id="hero-heading">
              高齢者と視覚障害者のための<br>やさしいネットスーパー
            </h1>
            <p class="hero-desc">
              大きな文字・音声操作・シンプルな操作で、誰でも安心してお買い物できます。
              お子様が遠くからサポートすることもできます。
            </p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
              <a href="#products" class="btn-primary" aria-label="商品一覧を見る">
                🛒 商品を見る
              </a>
              <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="startVoiceSearch()" aria-label="音声で注文する">
                🎤 音声で注文する
              </button>
            </div>

            <!-- Stats -->
            <div class="hero-stats" role="region" aria-label="サービス実績">
              <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-number">5,000+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">商品数</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-number">翌日</div>
                <div class="stat-label">配達可能</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-number">24h</div>
                <div class="stat-label">サポート</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right visual -->
          <div class="hero-visual" role="img" aria-label="やさしい買い物のイメージ：ショッピングカート・野菜・果物">
            <div style="font-size:4rem;">🛒</div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;font-size:2.5rem;">
              🥦 🍎 🥛 💊
            </div>
            <p>いつでも、どこでも、やさしく。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== VOICE SEARCH ===== -->
  <section id="voice-search" aria-labelledby="voice-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="voice-search-box">
        <h2 id="voice-heading">🎤 音声・テキスト検索</h2>
        <p>商品名を話しかけるか、テキストで入力してください</p>
        <div class="search-input-group" role="search">
          <input
            type="search"
            id="search-input"
            placeholder="例：牛乳、パン、解熱剤..."
            aria-label="商品を検索する"
            oninput="filterProducts(this.value)"
          />
          <button
